apple_vendor_description: On Apple devices, the medium-dark skin tone raising hands emoji conveys jubilant celebration with its subtly shaded, rounded digits.  The signature Apple 3D rendering gives the hands a sense of volume and movement, as if caught mid-raise in a moment of pure excitement. This emoji, seen on Apple devices, is perfect for expressing triumph, agreement, or enthusiastic participation in digital conversations.
